  fhir:description [ fhir:v "This ConceptMap maps vaccine codes from the Nuva terminology to the corresponding codes in the old swiss vaccines CodeSystem. It is generated based on the provided CSV mapping file and the Swissmedic CodeSystem."] ; # 
